rows.label: qst001401_msg0001
rows.name:
Aaah, why army of Superbia
not more speedy...?

rows.label: qst001401_msg0002
rows.name:
If things keep go like this, my precious
cargo spoil before it reach capital...

rows.label: qst001401_msg0003
rows.name:
Oho! What my eyes see,
if not Driver with time to spare!

rows.label: qst001401_msg0004
rows.name: Dear Driver, me have a request!

rows.label: qst001401_msg0005
rows.name:
Stuff that arrive here in Port Anangham
get taken into Alba Margen via
Downtown High Street, over yon.

rows.label: qst001401_msg0006
rows.name:
But right now, Cargo Transportation
Zone infested with Land Volff and
Noog Skeeter. Not safe for working!

rows.label: qst001401_msg0007
rows.name:
I ask Superbian soldiers there to
help with mop up but it look like it
take some time still...

rows.label: qst001401_msg0008
rows.name:
Make long story short, friends look
like they ready to go anytime, so
Pidede ask friends for help.

rows.label: qst001401_msg0009
rows.name:
If friends perform in speedy manner,
friends receive ample reward! It very
good deal, yes?

rows.label: qst001401_msg0011
rows.name:
Well then, please go beat up nasty
Land Volff and Noog Skeeter in
Cargo Transportation Zone!
